{"tid":2154714,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"莫少聰返強國山區做慈善 不幸腫成豬頭","createTime":"2020-08-13T09:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T11:05:38.000Z","uid":215823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c218320aa21d7abb739107fe55233a9b7681b4e2","tid":2154714,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:38:22.000Z","msg":"近日不少港星在大陸參加扶貧工作，之前有「烏鴉」張耀揚開抖音賬戶，上載返大陸做慈善的片段，當中他更土豪地現兜兜派人仔畀當地村民，而莫少聰與張敏亦有份一齊去做義工，幫手送物資絡山區居民。<br />\n<br />\n莫少聰今早在酒店拍片，表示自己有高原反應，身體不適，見片中的他眼腫及面腫，而聲音亦聽到沙啞，他表示仍然會堅持去做義工：「現在早上6點半，今天我覺得我有點高原反應，臉很腫，眼晴也腫，昨天睡覺也睡不好，只睡了兩、三小時，我的聲音也開始沙啞，不過今天我還要去探一些老人家，一些孤兒院、學生帶少少禮物送給他們，也希望這個高原反應快一點消失，加油。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4pDjsGY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4pDjsGY.png&h=4c57f166&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qSf2qtJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqSf2qtJ.png&h=50f32c25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PjFt5tM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPjFt5tM.png&h=3b2cf4db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a71fa0dbd87335646845e82bcc0c7a733813abd","tid":2154714,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EJzgCq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EJzgCq.jpg&h=49009c37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莫少聰兒子也出道當明星"},{"pid":"7eede316ae92a03ac7537a1dede12a1339ffd501","tid":2154714,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:05:38.000Z","msg":"又一個借「港星」名呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}